{"tid":529994,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行轉做Agent","createTime":"2018-01-15T10:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T12:49:22.000Z","uid":56803,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cfab682e3724775fc71e529a14107397a3858e65","tid":529994,"uid":56803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"自己係做retail bank, 預期一年內升RM <br />\n不過愈來愈覺得銀行制度同政策好惡啃<br />\n加上大環境趨勢下RM主要都要有保險數<br />\n既然殊途同歸加上有做保險既朋友<br />\n令我萌生轉做agent既念頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 做bank 2年 無人脈 無客帶走<br />\n口才有不過無Sell保險既exp<br />\n最擔心係source既問題 <br />\n亦係我覺得銀行既唯一優勢<br />\n而家23歲 想係26前年收入有50萬<br />\n<br />\n有無人有經驗可以share? <br />\n最好比較中立 <br />\n例如由rm轉做agent<br />\n或者由agent 入返bank做Specialist / Rm<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6799e3e29f1c2ce729a40ad0844c4ba059860c","tid":529994,"uid":89681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"調轉就大把人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8e4cd9e6704aaa1c0426e7616df35e0447c69f","tid":529994,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"講下你咩學歷做過咩啦"},{"pid":"d70955140ed27fe79162764fbfd6f875ee92e9b8","tid":529994,"uid":56803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c8e4cd9e6704aaa1c0426e7616df35e0447c69f","tid":529994,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"講下你咩學歷做過咩啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"Quit U no degree<br />\n2年bank, 半年綠區"},{"pid":"2f68980eedee6c5fa7cb6da22a88f3684bae6236","tid":529994,"uid":56803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6799e3e29f1c2ce729a40ad0844c4ba059860c","tid":529994,"uid":89681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"調轉就大把人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=